      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "T. s. Heskett an employee of the\nReview Publishing company and or\nganizer for the American Federation\nof Labor will acquire title to the\nLabor Journal on Monday IL present\nplans materialixe. The Labor Jour-\nnal is the official organ of the trades\ncouncil. but is owned by private indi-\nviduals. For the past six months 1t\nhas been owned and managed by d.\n\"A. Cartano and f. w. Harbaugh.\nThese gentlemen will have no inter-\nest In the paper in the future, which\nwill be published in the present form\nfor the present."
